title: Review of MMA 59 with Kamaru Usman
description:
Kamaru is the new UFC Welterweight champion after beating Tyrone Woodley in an epic 5 round battle. Usman displays a lot of character in his conversation with Rogan and is also a big fan of the podcast which is cool. Great conversation between these guys so check it out.
